<section class="project-content">
  <div class="container">
    <p>The first version we put up on the App Store had a very limited feature set, but it built the foundation for future versions of the app: take a picture of a bottle and add tasting notes. The camera flow have remained mostly unchanged since 2012. You start by taking a picture of a wine bottle, get a wine match, and optionally add a rating.</p>
  </div>
</section>

