    <h2>Designing for Android</h2>
    <p>I worked with an Android engineer and designed and built our first version of Delectable for Android right before Material Design was announced. After the Google I/O keynote in 2014 where Material Design was unveiled we went back to the drawing board and redesigned core parts of the app from scratch. Google awarded Delectable for Android with and Editor‘s Choice award as a result of the redesign.</p>
